posting_body: ['Welcome To The Heart of OlympiaNestled on a quiet residential street just minutes from the State Capitol, Capitol Crossing offers well designed one and two bedroom flat and loft-style apartment homes.', 'Living in the heart of Olympia offers close proximity to great restaurants, shops and recreational spots like the beautiful Capitol Lake.', 'Our homes include large decks, washers and dryers, gas fireplaces and much more.', 'Our unique lofts with spiral staircases, designer finishes and walkable location are just a few reasons why Capitol Crossing is an amazing community to come home to.', 'Check Availability', '-Quiet, Residential Neighborhood', '-Large Closets', '-Gas Fireplace', '-Patio/Balcony', '-On Bus Line', '-Washer/Dryer', '-Minutes', 'Away From State Capitol', '-Walking Distance To Downtown Olympia And Capitol Lake', '-Tiled', 'Accents', '-Reserved Parking', '-Ceiling Fan', '-Lofts With Spiral Staircase', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
